    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n      <strong>School:</strong>&nbsp;necromancy&nbsp;[fear, mind-affecting];\n    <br>\n    <strong>Level:</strong>&nbsp;Bard 2, Sorcerer 2, Wizard 2;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n    <br>\n    <strong>Components:</strong>&nbsp;V, S, M (a bit of bone from an undead skeleton, zombie, ghoul, ghast, or mummy)<br>\n    \n      <strong>Casting Time:</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Range:</strong>&nbsp;medium (100 ft. + 10 ft./level)<br>\n    \n    <strong>Target:</strong>&nbsp;one living creature per three levels, no two of which can be more than 30 ft. apart\n<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp;1 round/level or 1 round; see text for cause fear\n<br>\n    \n        <strong>Saving Throw:</strong>&nbsp;Will partial\n\n        <br>\n        <strong>Spell Resistance:</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  \n\n\n<p>\nThis spell functions like <i>cause fear, </i>except that it causes all targeted creatures of less than 6 HD to become frightened.\n</p><p><i>Material Component: </i>A bit of bone from an undead skeleton, zombie, ghoul, ghast, or mummy.\n</p>\n<hr/>\n\n\n\n</div>\n",
